== 硬件 ==
第四代iPad Air拥有全新的外觀，有新的天藍色和綠色，使用了与[[iPad_Pro|iPad Pro]]类似的全螢幕设计，，處理器採用[[5奈米製程|5奈米製程]]的全新[[Apple_A14|A14仿生處理器]]，使用了[[USB-C|USB-C]]接口，支援第二代[[Apple_Pencil|Apple Pencil]]、[[巧控鍵盤|巧控鍵盤]]和智慧型摺套連鍵盤。[[Touch_ID|Touch ID]]则内嵌到了顶部电源按钮中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=New iPad Air 4 (2020) release date, price, and everything you need to know {{!}} TechRadar|url=https://www.techradar.com/amp/news/new-ipad-air-4-2020|access-date=2020-09-15|website=www.techradar.com|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916164850/https://www.techradar.com/amp/news/new-ipad-air-4-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Warren|first=Tom|date=2020-09-15|title=Apple announces new iPad Air that looks more like an iPad Pro, starting at $599|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/15/21436500/apple-ipad-air-new-design-features-colors-release-date-price|access-date=2020-09-15|website=The Verge|language=|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915181529/https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/15/21436500/apple-ipad-air-new-design-features-colors-release-date-price|dead-url=no}}</ref>

