== Touch ID ==
因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|-{zh-cn:2019冠状病毒病;zh-hk:2019冠狀病毒病;zh-mo:2019冠狀病毒病;zh-tw:嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎;zh-my:2019冠状病毒病;zh-sg:2019冠状病毒疾病;}-疫情]]的影響，設備採用在開關按鈕中集成[[指紋識別|指紋識別]]裝置用於解鎖設備，因為在疫情流行期間使用者戴著[[口罩|口罩]]會使[[面部識別|面部識別]]變得沒有意義。<ref name="Tibken 2020">{{cite web | last=Tibken | first=Shara | title=iPhone 12 and the Touch ID button: Why Apple probably won't give it to us this year | website=CNET | date=October 13, 2020 | url=https://www.cnet.com/news/iphone-12-and-the-touch-id-button-why-apple-probably-wont-give-it-to-us-this-year/ | access-date=October 21, 2020 | archive-date=2020-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123065353/https://www.cnet.com/news/iphone-12-and-the-touch-id-button-why-apple-probably-wont-give-it-to-us-this-year/ }}</ref><ref name="Collins 2020">{{cite web | last=Collins | first=Katie | title=Our masks make Face ID useless. iPhone 12 did nothing to fix it | website=CNET | date=October 20, 2020 | url=https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-iphone-12-no-touch-id-button-face-id-useless-in-age-of-coronavirus-wearing-masks/ | access-date=October 20, 2020 | archive-date=2020-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123065356/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-iphone-12-no-touch-id-button-face-id-useless-in-age-of-coronavirus-wearing-masks/ }}</ref>

